Idea
The idea is to make a pure object oriented language to easy create games, with an inspiration of Fenix, and creating a easy syntax to call with object orientation

Description
* Documentation: in this folder you can view the latex documentation about our idea of this language
* vm: In this folder you can found the sourcecode of the virtual Machine
* Compilador: In this folder you can found the sourcecode of the Compiler

PreRequisits:
* Bisson
* G++
* CMake
* make/Xcode/Kdevelop...


Build:
In the VM and Compilador folder you have CMake files to build it.

You can found documentation about CMake here: http://www.cmake.org/cmake/help/cmake-2-8-docs.html

The summary is that:
cmake .
make


